name: Naruto: I Have a Gravity Training Room
summary: Natsuki arrived in the world of Naruto. He chose to let go of the savior complex, respect the fate of the chosen one, and live only for himself.Naruto: Sasuke!Sasuke: Naruto!Sakura: Stop it, you two! Dont fight anymore!The rain poured relentlessly. Off to the side, Natsuki snacked on sunflower seeds, casually handing some over to his girlfriend, Tenten.Pain: He deflected my Shinra Tensei!Obito: I just wanted to create a world with Rin... but that bastard Natsuki said If theres Rin, there has to be Kakashi, and made me watch Kakashi unleash Kirin. Be born already!Six Paths Madara: I acknowledge Natsuki as the strongest!Black Zetsu: Natsuki, you bastard! Get your foot off my mothers head!Natsuki: Just Eighth Gate, Hiraishin, and Sage Modeand Im already the strongest in the shinobi world? Really?
author: Zaelum
